<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0">
<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no, address=no, email=no">
<title>현대해상다이렉트</title>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../_ui_include/head.js"></script><!-- //Include: head -->
<script>
	$(function() {
		UI.init();

		$('.btn_samples').find('.btn').click();
	});
</script>
</head>
<body data-channel="mobile" data-login="false" data-category="login">
	<!-- wrap -->
	<div id="wrap">
		<!-- navbar -->
		<div id="header" class="navbar">
			<div class="header_wrap">
				<button type="button" class="btn_page_prev" aria-label="이전"></button>
				<h1 class="header_title">로그인</h1>
				<button type="button" class="btn_sidebar_open" aria-label="메뉴 열기"></button>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- //navbar -->
		<script type="text/javascript" src="../_ui_include/sidebar.js"></script><!-- Include: sidebar -->
		<div id="container">
			<!-- [Start of content] ================================== -->
			<div id="content">
				<!-- content_wrap -->
				<div class="content_wrap">
					<div class="section">
						<div class="governing">
							<h2 class="governing_title">Modal</h2>
						</div>
						<div class="comp">
							<div class="btn_area cta btn_samples">
								<a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="javascript:layerPop.open($('#MCOCO0003U'));" class="btn fill01">Open</a>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<!-- //content_wrap -->
			</div>
			<!-- [End of content] ==================================== -->
		</div>

		<!-- [Start of Modal] ====================================== -->
		<!-- Modal Full -->
		<div class="modal full fade" id="MCOCO0003U" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
			<div class="modal_dialog" role="document">
				<div class="modal_content">
					<div class="modal_header">
						<div class="wrapper">
							<h2 class="modal_title">네이버인증</h2>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="modal_body">
						<!-- wrapper: modal_body -->
						<div class="wrapper">
							<div class="section">
								<div class="governing ta_l">
									<h2 class="governing_title">네이버 앱으로 <br>본인인증을 진행해 주세요.</h2>
								</div>
								<div class="comp">
									<!-- [04/03] gap_lg 추가 -->
                  <div class="form_area gap_lg">
										<div class="form_item col2">
											<div class="form_label"><label for="inp02">주민등록번호/외국인등록번호</label></div>
											<div class="form_wrap">
												<input type="text" id="inp02" placeholder="앞 6자리">
											</div>
											<div class="form_wrap form_key">
												<div class="pin_area">
													<strong class="active"><span class="blind">1번째 번호</span></strong>
                          <strong><span class="blind">2번째 번호</span></strong>
                          <strong><span class="blind">3번째 번호</span></strong>
                          <strong><span class="blind">4번째 번호</span></strong>
                          <strong><span class="blind">5번째 번호</span></strong>
                          <strong><span class="blind">6번째 번호</span></strong>
													<strong><span class="blind">7번째 번호</span></strong>
												</div>
											</div>
											<div class="form_msg error">주민등록번호/외국인등록번호 앞 6자리를 꼭 입력해주세요.</div>
											<div class="form_msg error">주민등록번호/외국인등록번호 뒤 7자리를 꼭 입력해주세요.</div>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>

							<div class="section bottom_fix">
								<div class="comp">
									<div class="accordion notice full">
										<div class="item">
											<div class="fold_header">
												<a href="javascript:void(0);" role="button" title="내용보기">
													<div class="title"><strong>유의사항</strong></div>
													<i class="icon_angle"><span>내용보기/내용닫기</span></i>
												</a>
											</div>
											<div class="fold_body uol_list fz_sm">
												<ul>
													<li>네이버인증을 하려면 반드시 최신 버전의 네이버 앱이 설치되어 있어야 합니다.</li>
													<li>고객님의 아이디로 네이버 앱이 로그인되어 있어야 인증이 가능합니다.</li>
													<li>네이버 앱 또는 스마트폰 [설정]에서 푸시알림을 받을 수 있도록 설정해 주세요.</li>
													<li>네이버 앱을 재설치하거나 스마트폰을 바꾸신 경우,  네이버인증서 삭제 후 재발급하셔야 합니다.</li>
												</ul>
											</div>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
						<!-- //wrapper: modal_body -->
					</div>
					<div class="modal_footer fix">
						<div class="btn_area footer">
							<button type="button" class="btn fill01">인증 요청</button>
						</div>
						<div class="btn_area sub">
							<button type="button" class="btn text"><span>다른 방법 선택</span></button>
						</div>
					</div>
					<button type="button" class="btn_modal_close" aria-label="Close" onclick="layerPop.close('#MCOCO0003U'); return false;"><span>닫기</span></button>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<!-- //Modal Full -->
		<!-- [End of Modal] ======================================== -->
	</div>
	<!-- //wrap -->
</body>
</html>